results.name: Decimal expansion of length/width of a 2nd electrum rectangle.
comment: See A188619 for the definition of 2nd electrum rectangle.  Briefly, it is a rectangle such that the removal of a silver rectangle from one end leaves a golden rectangle.
link: Clark Kimberling, A Visual Euclidean Algorithm, The Mathematics Teacher 76 (1983) 108-109.
results.author: _Clark Kimberling_, Apr 06 2011
